{"tid":1380552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5 三罷 8月5 三罷 8月5 三罷","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T19:22:58.000Z","uid":233325,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d69fe999b0e66466d336e13c3697c42eb6c5b1d3","tid":1380552,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFgFt9d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFgFt9d.png&h=2587b7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjAV2uf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjAV2uf.png&h=3ec23c96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到而家連登有好多三罷嘅post<br />\n知道大家都明白點解要三罷<br />\n但係不如寫封短短地嘅公開信，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>解釋初衷，呼籲人響應</strong></span><br />\n我文筆唔太好，暫時諗到應該講：<br />\n經過一個月嘅抗爭，和平遊行集會試過，激烈嘅衝擊亦都試過，政府依然無示市民意見。<br />\n更變本加厲，執法者以過分武力以圖鎮壓，亦大肆清算拘捕，整做白色恐怖。<br />\n一個又一個記者會，清楚顯示特區政府將幾塊玻璃、一個徽號嘅價值睇得重於有血有肉有靈魂嘅香港人<br />\n面對政府一次又一次嘅不平等對待，眼看一次又一次嘅不公義事件，政府一次又一次無視遊行示威，你還能保持沈默嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果真係罷工不如而家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>聯絡政黨、團體、各大機構、各大工會</strong></span><br />\n有冇人做緊<br />\n有冇人嘗試過可以點做<br />\n不如請佢地帶起罷工，有大機構牽頭，其他小公司會易啲響應"},{"pid":"855312a46842af8bb9853348e3c60245cf527fde","tid":1380552,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d99173931974ffdb6acf4f399e62d47c64c8c6","tid":1380552,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji